profile:
Home to the Fraser Valley's finest quality and value in the kitchen, bath & storage space. 

We hand select all our cabinets, countertops & accessories, choosing only those we would use in our own homes.

Our design team works with you to provide a fun, creative experience with friendly, professional advice & project management services to help you realize the perfect space paying close attention to the design aesthetic and its'  final form & function. 

Our trusted craftsmen and certified technicians are selected for their professional, efficient, personable service with attention to detail that helps ensure a stress free project.

The Littler Cabinet Shop is the winner of the Favourite Cabinet Shop as voted by you in The Progress Newspapers "2014 Chilliwack A-List" . We carry full liability insurance & complete Worksafe BC coverage for your piece of mind.
